============================
RedirectPost
----------------------------
- Requirements
cakePHP 3

- Installation
$ composer require adrianodemoura/redirect-post

- Usage

In Controller:

$this->loadComponent('RedirectPost');

$data = $this->request->getData();
$this->RedirectPost->save( ['action'=>'acton_target'], $data);

$data = $this->RedirectPost->read();


